docs.title: Commands
docs.text: Hi * mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. * mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. * mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. * mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit.

docs.title: Project layout
docs.text:
mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.
docs/
    index.md  # The documentation homepage.
    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.
